    "text": "COVID-19 Disinformation Research and Reporting Act of 2021\n\nThis bill requires the National Science Foundation to contract with the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine to study disinformation and misinformation about COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) on the internet and social media platforms."
